author: @luckyonekadii4220
text: KAI:   I don’t know. I just stay alone quietly like this. I really like listening to music and recalling images. For example, in the darkness if a water droplet falls it will splatter. I will spread the image from there gradually. In times like that, I add colour while thinking. There are also times when it is black and white.

author: @luckyonekadii4220
text: KAI: For concert performances, I consider the mood and lyrics of a song, and for my solo stages I put in my own emotions. Title tracks have distinct choreography and pairing with other members. If there’s an importance to lyrics, there are no limitations of solo stages. If it’s sad, the dance gets sad too. But even if it’s sad, you dance in a way that makes you feel good, so the people watching will recieve the emotion and also feel good.

author: @luckyone_kadi7162
text: KAI:    Overall, I feel comfortable and free on stage. Moving my body is the comfortable part, but the emotions I feel are new every time. There are choreographies that I dance happily and have fun, and there are choreographies that I dance to relay a message or feelings.

author: @xavierii337
text:
This is for all the people that are unaware about KAI & his music being nominated for multiple awards & additional details:
Please vote for KAI's "Mmmh" on M Wave's website: https://www.mwave.me/en/vote/mcountdown/vote . Voting ends on December 14th.
It's for M COUNTDOWN PRE VOTING. It seems like another music show.  You could sign-in with a social account: KAKAO, Twitter, NAVER, LINE, Facebook, Tumblr, Google, weibo.com, & We Chat. 1 vote per account, though. You could use as many accounts you want to vote for KAI. 

If you are a fan of EXO and/or KAI, please help support this brother by voting for him wherever he's nominated. 
You could also download the apps, CHOEAEDOL, IDOL CHAMP, FanPlus, MuBeat, Whosfan, V Live, etc. from the Google Play Store & Apple Store. 
Here's at least 3 websites from KAI's trusted fanbases: stationkai.com , erigomnation.com & kaivoting.page . 
KAI's solo fandom's name is Erigom (L bear), but he often refers to his fans as EXO-L or Eris & other variations of the name. 
EXO's fandom name is EXO-L (EXO-Love). 
Of course, if you can, please continue to stream all of KAI's solo music videos & other solo related videos, including his solo performance videos, because views are included in the voting criteria. 
You don't have to do anything you don't want to do, but it would greatly appreciated if you could join us in helping to support the new solo artist, KAI aka Kim Jong-in. It would be a wonderful early birthday gift. His birthday is on January 14th.  

Kim Jong-in aka KAI deserves for us to at least try to vote & help him win some awards for working very hard to give us his solo project & all this extra content that we didn't know we wanted, but we are glad we received it. It's just a way to show your gratitude. 
I'm sure he'll appreciate us making an effort, although he is very humble & didn't ask us for anything in return. 
However, like any other artist, he just wants people check out & appreciate him, his art & his other work. 
As you can see, this brother is very passionate about his craft. I haven't noticed him do anything halfway. Also, he's a perfectionist, who is sometimes too hard on himself, although everyone else thought he did an amazing job. 
He's even not afraid to express his emotions in a society with some people who often give some males a hard time for being in tuned with their emotions & sensitive side. He's not afraid to breakdown gender barriers either. He's a very artistic, quirky, intelligent, hilarious, kind-hearted & down to earth, respectable, personable, & multitalented guy. 
This is the same guy that was surprised that he had more international fans than he thought did & that a lot people enjoyed his dancing, his work, & him in general. 
Just watch some of his latest videos & feel him out for yourself. You'll see the type of person he is for yourself. He's a stand up guy. 
KAI is just a stage name & a charismatic idol persona, Kim Jong-in is the complex man behind the "KAI" image, & Nini is the very soft & shy side of Kim Jong-in. His duality is something special. 

Also, he's doing a lot of self-promoting activities almost like an independent artist & some things he wanted to do for himself, his family & loved ones, & his fans. This solo project is KAI aka Kim Jong-in's baby. SM finally gave him more creative freedom to what he wanted to do. 
Therefore, it's KAI's vision, not SM's doing. What you see & get is coming from KAI & his team. Don't give SM too much credit when they don't deserve it. Moreover, KAI invested his blood, sweat & tears into his solo project, especial his own money.

Anyway, if you are interested & use Twitter, Facebook & Instagram, please search for more info. Even Google, if it's necessary. 
It's OK to watch his introduction guides to learn more about KAI aka Kim Jong-in, but please make sure you pick good up to date ones. 
Follow KAI's Instagram account: zkdlin @ instagram.com/zkdlin . 
Again, here's at least 3 websites from KAI's trusted fanbases: stationkai.com , erigomnation.com & kaivoting.page .  
A lot information is available on these websites. They have more, but I don't know them all, sorry. These are the main ones I know. 
Reminder: KAI's solo fandom's name is Erigom (L bear), but he often refers to his fans as EXO-L or Eris & other variations of the name. 
EXO's fandom name is EXO-L (EXO-Love). 
Here's a website that offers some basic info about Kim Jong-in aka KAI & is often used by some new fans: https://kprofiles.com/kai-profile-facts-kai-ideal-type/ . 
Last but not least, please feel free to ask his most knowledgeable fans, some Erigoms & EXO-Ls since they are the ones who support KAI the most. Keyword: Some, not all.

author: @logant2838
text:
Thank you, Kim Jongin aka KAI & team.

KAI's solo debut album, 'The 1st Mini Album - KAI (开),' will be released on Monday, November 30th. 
Watch his album's preview trailer, "FILM: KAI," ( https://youtu.be/VjjKbrFJoxY ), to get a taste of more of his solo music, his vocals & performance, his artistic concept, his duality, & more. 
It's an unforgettable experience. I'm still shook, & I can't stop watching it. 
Also, this mood sampler is an instrumental of his B-side track, "Amnesia," & the version with his vocals is revealed more in his highlight/medley trailer, "FILM: KAI," along with other songs from his album, ''The 1st Mini Album - KAI (开).' 
Oh my God, my eyes, my ears, & my mind were truly blessed. I feel delivered. 

If you enjoy the KAI's artistic & duality journey, please support him, stream & buy his solo music, & vote for him. 
Please check out more of Kim Jongin aka KAI & his solo work
Follow Kim Jongin aka KAI on his Instagram: @zkdlin. 
Follow his music bands' EXO & SuperM on Twitter: @weareoneEXO & @superm.
Follow his music groups' EXO & SuperM on Instagram: @weareone.exo & @superm.

So the decision of what size and who to work with is not entirely provided by the company, but is of course made after the album's earnings are settled, and the investment funds and expenses are deducted from it.

But KAI's first solo, the full-length music video is of such high quality that it really doesn't take into account the profits or money, just the quality of the album.

Tears welled up when I thought about the work Jongin had been preparing for so long.

That's why I'm going to buy more albums. TT TT That's all I can do as a fan.

author: @nadiamartinez5803
text:
It's seems like a lot of you survived KAI's solo album highlight/medley teaser trailer, "FILM: KAI." (https://youtu.be/VjjKbrFJoxY) 
If you haven't watched "FILM: KAI,' by KAI, a visual-audio masterpiece already, please do it. You won't regret it. It's worth every second. 

I'm surprised I survived it. Now I know this instrumental is for his song, "Amnesia." I loved all his song snippets that played in every scene of his trailer. I can't wait to hear the full songs. It's hard to pick just one favorite song, when I like them all.
Kim KAI served vocals & more, honey. I'm glad KAI is being appreciated more for his vocals & not just his dancing & visuals. He is an ARTISTE. He's a humble multitalented king, & I'm very proud of him. I've been watching all KAI & EXO related videos, getting my life.

author: @kimjongdae1880
text:
How to str3am on YouTube
(source: https://youtu.be/fvqripLDs7k):
Do
- log into YouTube manually
- search the video manually
- leave a like
- leave a positive comment
- watch in all the browsers
- watch the whole video
- use playlist when busy or sleeping, but not in first 24 hours (put on list loop and make sure they are 2-3 mvs in the middle of them, I prefer 1billion vi3ws, Hello, and Telephone or any EXO mvs)
- watch on as many devices as possible such as computer, tablet, phone, etc.
Don't
- say anything like "str3am" or "vi3ws" on the comment section (it attracts the YouTube moderators into the idea that we are bots)
- pause or skip anything
- mute the video ( low to medium is fine)
- have to many tabs 
- go on incognito
- refresh the page over and over
